RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

92-2164. Lorain Cty. Bar Assn. v. Motsch.

Reported at 74 Ohio St.3d 1487, 658 N.E.2d 306. On motion for reconsideration. Motion denied.

Douglas, Resnick and Pfeifer, JJ., dissent.

On petition to dismiss by the Commission on Continuing Legal Education. Petition granted.
